Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.26,0:08:10.49,Default,,0,0,0,,敵軍坦克正在逼近第一防線陣地
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.34,0:08:13.70,Default,,0,0,0,,炮兵隊都沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.92,0:08:14.33,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.61,0:08:17.04,Default,,0,0,0,,把修正坐標發過去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.48,0:08:19.93,Default,,0,0,0,,讓日耳曼佬嚐嚐榴彈雨的滋味
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.25,0:08:22.96,Default,,0,0,0,,射擊指揮所 這裡是中隊總部
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.53,0:08:29.61,Default,,0,0,0,,效力射坐標5200 觀測方位角400
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.80,0:08:33.73,Default,,0,0,0,,中隊效力射 齊射準備
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.24,0:08:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,開火
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.89,0:08:46.49,Default,,0,0,0,,我方有取勝的希望嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.36,0:08:51.23,Default,,0,0,0,,能給後方齊爾特菲的居民爭取到避難時間
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.74,0:08:52.60,Default,,0,0,0,,就算很不錯的了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.36,0:08:55.47,Default,,0,0,0,,只能爭取一點時間嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.93,0:08:58.00,Default,,0,0,0,,要塞的士兵們都知道嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.88,0:09:01.28,Default,,0,0,0,,他們應該知道這點仍在作戰
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.98,0:09:08.96,Default,,0,0,0,,只是為了…爭取時間 就要賠上士兵們的性命嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.41,0:09:52.20,Default,,0,0,0,,沒有什麼我能做的事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.29,0:09:55.69,Default,,0,0,0,,為了仍然在不斷犧牲的他們
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.06,0:10:01.62,Default,,0,0,0,,可惡 可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.31,0:10:03.20,Default,,0,0,0,,喂 你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.39,0:10:05.50,Default,,0,0,0,,過來 來這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.12,0:10:08.20,Default,,0,0,0,,你是第二分隊的吧 叫什麼名字
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.74,0:10:09.64,Default,,0,0,0,,我叫喬納斯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.03,0:10:14.12,Default,,0,0,0,,好 你能做機槍助手吧 準備迎戰
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.76,0:10:15.17,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.78,0:10:29.34,Default,,0,0,0,,子彈
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.51,0:10:29.99,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.50,0:10:41.89,Default,,0,0,0,,中隊長下令 棄守第一防線陣地
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.32,0:10:44.76,Default,,0,0,0,,撤退至第二防線陣地
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.33,0:10:48.87,Default,,0,0,0,,終於下令了嗎 我們撤
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.87,0:10:52.61,Default,,0,0,0,,棄守第一防線陣地
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.54,0:11:04.26,Default,,0,0,0,,爸爸 媽媽 艾米爾 海地 海蓮娜…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.78,0:11:09.60,Default,,0,0,0,,爸爸 媽媽 艾米爾 海地 海蓮娜…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.37,0:11:13.94,Default,,0,0,0,,還沒攻下來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.39,0:11:17.21,Default,,0,0,0,,是 敵軍陣地背後的炮擊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.46,0:11:19.79,Default,,0,0,0,,應該是有山頂彈著觀測員的輔助
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.29,0:11:24.08,Default,,0,0,0,,炮彈相當精準地阻擊了我軍的前進
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.44,0:11:26.57,Default,,0,0,0,,可惡的傢伙們
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.24,0:11:29.45,Default,,0,0,0,,中將 時間拖太久的話
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.60,0:11:31.67,Default,,0,0,0,,陛下恐怕會不高興的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.87,0:11:33.22,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.64,0:11:37.80,Default,,0,0,0,,凱勒少校 我請求空軍再加一輪支援轟炸
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.43,0:11:39.94,Default,,0,0,0,,把觀測點摧毀
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.21,0:11:41.67,Default,,0,0,0,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.77,0:11:45.48,Default,,0,0,0,,勝利的美酒還是讓我們一同品嚐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.82,0:12:05.15,Default,,0,0,0,,把能找到的都搬過來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.44,0:12:08.00,Default,,0,0,0,,這些東西說不定也能派上點用場
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.93,0:12:15.44,Default,,0,0,0,,公主殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.41,0:12:21.13,Default,,0,0,0,,求您了 讓我們去凱寧貝格吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.62,0:12:22.60,Default,,0,0,0,,打消這念頭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.28,0:12:26.54,Default,,0,0,0,,那裡有我們的戰友 我們無法坐視不理
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.12,0:12:28.75,Default,,0,0,0,,連點像樣的裝備都沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.88,0:12:31.40,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼可能在敵人眼前過河啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.06,0:12:33.79,Default,,0,0,0,,不論是刺刀還是匕首
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.93,0:12:35.68,Default,,0,0,0,,能多殺一個敵人都好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.16,0:12:38.29,Default,,0,0,0,,要塞裡的戰友都已經戰死了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.03,0:12:40.92,Default,,0,0,0,,我們無法再看著他們也去送死
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.01,0:12:42.57,Default,,0,0,0,,求您了 公主殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.93,0:12:44.38,Default,,0,0,0,,喂 給我適可而止…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.38,0:12:44.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我不同意
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.47,0:12:49.38,Default,,0,0,0,,現在的我們什麼都做不了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.82,0:12:50.46,Default,,0,0,0,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.96,0:12:54.16,Default,,0,0,0,,不要忘記了 我們要完成的事是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.88,0:12:56.73,Default,,0,0,0,,我們到底該為了什麼而拚命
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.92,0:13:03.05,Default,,0,0,0,,既不是為了復仇 也不是白白去送死
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.64,0:13:07.60,Default,,0,0,0,,而是為了保護人民 保護我們的家人啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.82,0:13:11.95,Default,,0,0,0,,戰況現在極其嚴峻
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.54,0:13:17.17,Default,,0,0,0,,總有一天 我也會命令你們拼上性命去保護祖國的子民
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.98,0:13:20.51,Default,,0,0,0,,可是現在還不是時候
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.56,0:13:22.19,Default,,0,0,0,,請忍耐下去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.53,0:13:27.86,Default,,0,0,0,,凱寧貝格的將士們在為爭取時間而誓死戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.20,0:13:30.95,Default,,0,0,0,,我們該撤退的時候就要撤退
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.81,0:13:37.44,Default,,0,0,0,,對不起 現在的我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.15,0:13:40.65,Default,,0,0,0,,就連為各位找塊殉國的地點都辦不到
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.52,0:13:44.62,Default,,0,0,0,,本來我不該告訴你們該如何犧牲
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.62,0:13:46.08,Default,,0,0,0,,而是該如何活下去才是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.06,0:13:50.86,Default,,0,0,0,,為你們建造一個只需要關注明天生活的國家
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.55,0:13:53.25,Default,,0,0,0,,明明這才是我的職責
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.76,0:13:55.64,Default,,0,0,0,,公主殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.02,0:13:58.56,Default,,0,0,0,,原諒我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.48,0:14:12.83,Default,,0,0,0,,原諒這個無力的我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.86,0:14:48.27,Default,,0,0,0,,是 恐怕只是時間的問題了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.22,0:14:51.16,Default,,0,0,0,,但是士兵們還在…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.65,0:14:55.61,Default,,0,0,0,,是 我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.48,0:14:58.24,Default,,0,0,0,,中將？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.50,0:15:01.84,Default,,0,0,0,,準備撤退
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.74,0:15:06.16,Default,,0,0,0,,退到瓦格斯重建防線
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.13,0:15:16.85,Default,,0,0,0,,下士
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.60,0:15:31.61,Default,,0,0,0,,增援已經到了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.34,0:15:35.06,Default,,0,0,0,,轟炸很快就要開始了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.62,0:15:37.44,Default,,0,0,0,,這下就將軍了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.65,0:15:42.37,Default,,0,0,0,,本來可以的話 我倒不想多麻煩你們
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.77,0:15:48.00,Default,,0,0,0,,無論如何 勝利屬於我們大日耳曼是不會變的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.14,0:15:50.13,Default,,0,0,0,,帝國勝利永存
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.23,0:15:52.43,Default,,0,0,0,,帝國勝利永存
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.72,0:16:31.27,Default,,0,0,0,,去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.81,0:16:36.92,Default,,0,0,0,,那是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.21,0:16:38.10,Default,,0,0,0,,管它是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.61,0:16:41.06,Default,,0,0,0,,能為我們擊落斯圖卡的就是友軍
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.80,0:16:44.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我們還沒兵臨絕路呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.12,0:16:54.07,Default,,0,0,0,,芬妮殿下 凱寧貝格那邊…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.86,0:17:37.17,Default,,0,0,0,,投下一枚炸彈也好！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.35,0:17:40.01,Default,,0,0,0,,拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.99,0:18:16.94,Default,,0,0,0,,喂 你沒事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.96,0:18:20.78,Default,,0,0,0,,是 我沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.26,0:18:24.95,Default,,0,0,0,,請問 我聽說這裡堆著很多古劍之類的裝備
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.37,0:18:26.18,Default,,0,0,0,,都堆在哪裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.68,0:18:28.70,Default,,0,0,0,,那些劍都在那裡…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.12,0:18:30.90,Default,,0,0,0,,糟了 堆在上面嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.49,0:18:33.58,Default,,0,0,0,,多謝了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.81,0:18:36.73,Default,,0,0,0,,還有 我可以借用一下這個嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.83,0:18:38.72,Default,,0,0,0,,這怎麼行呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.23,0:18:40.12,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.62,0:18:44.59,Default,,0,0,0,,等一下我會好好謝罪的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.56,0:19:31.19,Default,,0,0,0,,各位
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.68,0:19:35.29,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼可能
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.56,0:19:47.15,Default,,0,0,0,,接下來是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.30,0:20:03.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我的天啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.57,0:20:06.75,Default,,0,0,0,,發生什麼事了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.39,0:20:08.39,Default,,0,0,0,,芬妮殿下…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.20,0:20:14.09,Default,,0,0,0,,是伊澤塔嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.86,0:20:16.78,Default,,0,0,0,,她到底是什麼人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.40,0:20:21.42,BackGround,,0,0,0,,太誇張了吧 敵我都陷入混亂了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.85,0:20:19.56,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼你願意做到那種地步
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.77,0:20:24.54,Default,,0,0,0,,你的心情 我絕不會讓它白費
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.24,0:20:26.71,Default,,0,0,0,,漢斯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.57,0:20:29.37,Default,,0,0,0,,有方法能從這裡將我的話
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.83,0:20:32.13,Default,,0,0,0,,傳達給凱寧貝格的將士們嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.40,0:20:39.41,Default,,0,0,0,,好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.77,0:20:42.08,Default,,0,0,0,,上士 是閃光信號
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.41,0:20:42.89,Default,,0,0,0,,你說什麼！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.53,0:20:49.69,Default,,0,0,0,,我是…奧特菲涅
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.42,0:20:51.16,Default,,0,0,0,,公主殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.33,0:20:56.01,Default,,0,0,0,,傳告我深愛的士兵們
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.24,0:21:01.97,Default,,0,0,0,,那個紅髮少女是我無可取代的友人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.89,0:21:06.69,Default,,0,0,0,,是守護我們的白色魔女的轉世
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.08,0:21:13.63,Default,,0,0,0,,請和她一同 守護我們祖國的自由吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.59,0:21:24.84,Default,,0,0,0,,白色魔女…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.70,0:21:27.99,Default,,0,0,0,,對了 是Weiss Hexe
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.65,0:21:30.89,Default,,0,0,0,,守護艾露史塔德的魔女啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.45,0:21:35.23,Default,,0,0,0,,好 我們也和魔女一起 衝啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.43,0:21:39.12,Default,,0,0,0,,別開這種不好笑的玩笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.54,0:21:45.26,Default,,0,0,0,,這是真的 戰車中隊16輛戰車被全數擊毀
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.19,0:21:57.08,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼可能
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.59,0:22:26.80,Default,,0,0,0,,對不起 公主殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.89,0:22:30.90,Default,,0,0,0,,我實在控制不了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.21,0:22:34.09,Default,,0,0,0,,大傻瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.68,0:22:38.24,Default,,0,0,0,,你真的好傻 伊澤塔
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.14,0:22:46.00,Default,,0,0,0,,還好你平安…謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.99,0:22:47.81,Default,,0,0,0,,公主殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.73,0:23:03.17,Default,,0,0,0,,魔女？你說什麼呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.66,0:23:05.14,Default,,0,0,0,,居然是芬妮殿下說的？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.58,0:23:08.01,Default,,0,0,0,,總之贏了對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.28,0:23:08.65,BackGround,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.65,0:23:10.80,Default,,0,0,0,,將這件事連同士兵的目擊證詞一起
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.53,0:23:15.18,Default,,0,0,0,,鉅細靡遺地全數呈報 用最快速度
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.92,0:23:18.18,Default,,0,0,0,,公主殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.56,0:23:20.27,Default,,0,0,0,,光榮屬於我們的魔女
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.85,0:23:23.82,Default,,0,0,0,,還有奧特菲涅公女殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.33,0:23:26.59,Default,,0,0,0,,為了艾露史塔德的自由
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.72,0:23:40.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs25\fnGen Jyuu Gothic LP Regular}Sieh, vor den grenzenden Bergen,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.43,0:23:46.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs25\fnGen Jyuu Gothic LP Regular}wird unser voller Stolz erwähnt.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.20,0:23:53.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs25\fnGen Jyuu Gothic LP Regular}Oh, Eylstadt, die Hügeln der Alpen,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.08,0:24:00.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs25\fnGen Jyuu Gothic LP Regular}von der Ewigkeit, dem schönen Wunsch,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.89,0:24:07.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs25\fnGen Jyuu Gothic LP Regular}Wanderrout(e) , unsere Welt,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.63,0:24:13.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs25\fnGen Jyuu Gothic LP Regular}der hoher Berg, unseres Feld,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.39,0:24:20.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs2\fnGen Jyuu Gothic LP Regular5}Oh, Eylstadt, Hügeln der Engeln,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.23,0:24:27.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs25\fnGen Jyuu Gothic LP Regular}von der Ruhe und Staat mit unserem Wunsch
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.72,0:23:40.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs35}看啊 毗鄰群山前方
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.43,0:23:46.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs35}吾等至上榮光彰揚
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.20,0:23:53.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs35}啊 艾露史塔特 阿爾卑斯山丘連綿
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.08,0:24:00.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs35}充滿了永恆和美好的夙願
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.89,0:24:07.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs35}漫漫征途 吾等開荒
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.63,0:24:13.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs35}高山峻岭 處處戰場
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.39,0:24:20.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs35}啊 艾露史塔特 天使降臨山間
